{{Infobox language |name=Kola |region=[[Aru Islands]] |speakers={{sigfig|7730|2}} |date=1995–2011 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Austronesian |fam2=[[Malayo-Polynesian languages|Malayo-Polynesian]] (MP) |fam3=[[Nuclear Malayo-Polynesian languages|Nuclear MP]] |fam4=([[Central–Eastern Malayo-Polynesian languages|Central–Eastern]]) |fam5=[[Aru languages|Aru]] |lc1=kvv|ld1=Kola |lc2=kvp|ld2=Kompane |glotto=kola1292 |glottorefname=Kola–Kompane }}
'''Kola''' is one of the [[Aru languages]], spoken by inhabitants of the [[Aru Islands]].
